name: Dr. Ernesto J. Perez
about:
Dr. Ernesto J. Perez earned his Bachelor of Science degree in biology before attending the University of Puerto Rico School of Dental Medicine, graduating in 1986. He continues to advance his training regularly through continuing education courses held through study clubs and through the American Dental AssociationÂ®. He has received advanced training in dental implants, and in 2020, he was a recipient of the Top Implant, Cosmetic, and General Dentist Award for Miami. He has practiced in the Miami area for over 35 years.

Dr. Perez was born in Pinar de Rio, Cuba. In 1967, he moved to Puerto Rico, and in 1987, he moved to south Florida, where he began practicing general and aesthetic dentistry.

clinic.name: Dr. Ernesto J. Perez, DMD
clinic.description:
Welcome to Dr. Ernesto Perez Miami! For over 35 years, our dentists and team have helped patients of all ages improve their oral health and smile with quality dental care. We are a family-oriented practice dedicated to providing comprehensive care that will improve your overall health as well as your smile, and you can count on us to take the time to understand your needs and provide you with unique and effective treatment plans.

General dentist office that offers a host of different services including (but not limited to) fillings, whitenings, implants, sedation, extractions, root canals, Invisalign, and cosmetic dentistry. We treat the whole family (including children and the elderly) and have been established and practicing in Miami for 32+ years!
